{"tid":497544,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[百份] 港媒抹黑澳門損和諧！強烈要求特府引《內部保安綱要法》禁止！","createTime":"2017-12-13T01:25:38.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-13T01:53:42.000Z","uid":23707,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"5b6fdcdcb6627e7e02074688bb59c466ab2a034f","tid":497544,"uid":23707,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-13T01:25:38.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/%E6%BE%B3%E9%96%80/%E6%B8%AF%E5%AA%92%E6%8A%B9%E9%BB%91%E6%BE%B3%E9%96%80%E6%90%8D%E5%92%8C%E8%AB%A7-%E5%BC%B7%E7%83%88%E8%A6%81%E6%B1%82%E7%89%B9%E5%BA%9C%E5%BC%95-%E5%85%A7%E9%83%A8%E4%BF%9D%E5%AE%89%E7%B6%B1%E8%A6%81%E6%B3%95-%E7%A6%81%E6%AD%A2/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2F%25E6%25BE%25B3%25E9%2596%2580%2F%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E5%25AA%2592%25E6%258A%25B9%25E9%25BB%2591%25E6%25BE%25B3%25E9%2596%2580%25E6%2590%258D%25E5%2592%258C%25E8%25AB%25A7-%25E5%25BC%25B7%25E7%2583%2588%25E8%25A6%2581%25E6%25B1%2582%25E7%2589%25B9%25E5%25BA%259C%25E5%25BC%2595-%25E5%2585%25A7%25E9%2583%25A8%25E4%25BF%259D%25E5%25AE%2589%25E7%25B6%25B1%25E8%25A6%2581%25E6%25B3%2595-%25E7%25A6%2581%25E6%25AD%25A2%2F&d=DGK2LAqmCD1msRExv7znd57TfgnX9jywtYe9GXZmhCU%3D&h=213ee493\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2F%25E6%25BE%25B3%25E9%2596%2580%2F%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E5%25AA%2592%25E6%258A%25B9%25E9%25BB%2591%25E6%25BE%25B3%25E9%2596%2580%25E6%2590%258D%25E5%2592%258C%25E8%25AB%25A7-%25E5%25BC%25B7%25E7%2583%2588%25E8%25A6%2581%25E6%25B1%2582%25E7%2589%25B9%25E5%25BA%259C%25E5%25BC%2595-%25E5%2585%25A7%25E9%2583%25A8%25E4%25BF%259D%25E5%25AE%2589%25E7%25B6%25B1%25E8%25A6%2581%25E6%25B3%2595-%25E7%25A6%2581%25E6%25AD%25A2%2F&h=8d4b348c\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.thestandnews.com/%E6%BE%B3%E9%96%80/%E6%B8%AF%E5%AA%92%E6%8A%B9%E9%BB%91%E6%BE%B3%E9%96%80%E6%90%8D%E5%92%8C%E8%AB%A7-%E5%BC%B7%E7%83%88%E8%A6%81%E6%B1%82%E7%89%B9%E5%BA%9C%E5%BC%95-%E5%85%A7%E9%83%A8%E4%BF%9D%E5%AE%89%E7%B6%B1%E8%A6%81%E6%B3%95-%E7%A6%81%E6%AD%A2/</a><br />\n<br />\n澳門近期新聞多多：蘇嘉豪被中止議員職務、文化局大地震、海關倒掛國旗、被列為避稅黑名單等等，可謂日日新鮮。而一海之隔的「方向報」，則不停出文炮轟澳門政府施政不力，力度比澳門傳媒來得更凶更猛，標題由最初的「澳門消息」變成之後的「澳門亂象」，再到日前終進化到登上A1頭條。<br />\n<br />\n澳門市民均議論紛紛，猜想「方向報」的舉動，會否是因為暴風雨即將來臨。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 但無論背後動機如何，本人對「方向報」連日來瘋狂揭澳門瘡疤的行為實在非常反感，完全有違澳門要和諧的發展路線。在澳門立立亂之時，港媒為增加曝光率及銷量，還要派人來澳為澳門添亂、斷章取義、抹黑澳門，是否嫌澳門還不夠亂？<br />\n<br />\n我最不喜歡港媒常以「新聞自由」作為口號，請你回去你的自由地方好嗎？澳門人只想用自己的方式救澳門，請勿在我們傷口上灑鹽。強烈要求特區政府引用《內部保安綱要法》禁止「方向報」記者入境，以免影響澳門的和諧穩定。<br />\n<br />\n最後加多句：曲的直不了，直的曲不了。"},{"pid":"badd71fbccbcc1542d10144aa25e48d7e4bb86a7","tid":497544,"uid":23707,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-13T01:26:17.000Z","msg":"回帶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/491874/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/491874/page/1</a>"},{"pid":"831bfa67e126e5022d64079d78ee157bed0397c2","tid":497544,"uid":22736,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-13T01:37:27.000Z","msg":"曲到圓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"850ba9c627bfeb291f97d280ac7173958e887dcc","tid":497544,"uid":23707,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-13T01:53:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}